text_raw:
2. The 20th day of July 2020 is appointed as the day on which the 
Microenterprise Loan Fund (Amendment) Act 2020 (No. 3 of 2020) shall come 
into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

20 July, 2020. 

LEO VARADKAR, 

Minister for Business, Enterprise and Innovation. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 4th August, 2020.
